# UI Components (6 Zones + Overlays)

**Priority:** P1
**Dependencies:** TYPE-Foundation, SETUP-Base

## Overview
Build all UI components for the 6 game zones plus overlay states. Components must be individually testable with Storybook-style state preview.

## Zone Components

### Zone 1: Power-Ups / Community Mechanics
```tsx
// src/components/shop/PowerUpSlots.tsx
interface PowerUpSlotsProps {
  slots: PowerUpSlot[];
  activePowerUp?: PowerUpType;
  onSlotClick: (slot: PowerUpSlot) => void;
}

type PowerUpSlot = {
  id: string;
  type: 'witness' | 'observer' | 'network';
  status: 'available' | 'cooldown' | 'locked';
  cooldownRemaining?: number;
};
```

**States to test:**
- All empty (locked)
- One available (blinking)
- One on cooldown (greyed, countdown)
- Three active (full)

### Zone 2: Customer Queue
```tsx
// src/components/shop/CustomerQueue.tsx
interface CustomerQueueProps {
  queue: QueueEntity[];
  visibleCount: number;
  onEntityClick: (entity: QueueEntity) => void;
}

type QueueEntity = Customer | Agent;
```

**States to test:**
- Empty queue
- Full queue (6 visible)
- Agent at front
- Agent in middle
- "..." indicator (more in queue)

### Zone 3: Melt-O-Meter
```tsx
// src/components/shop/MeltOMeter.tsx
interface MeltOMeterProps {
  level: HeatLevel;
  customerCount: number;
  communitySupport: SupportLevel;
  popularity: PopularityLevel;
  dayNumber: number;
}
```

**States to test:**
- Calm (green, low fill)
- Watched (yellow, medium fill)
- Tense (orange, high fill)
- Critical (red, full fill, drip animation)

### Zone 4: Shop Counter
```tsx
// src/components/shop/ShopCounter.tsx
interface ShopCounterProps {
  featuredFlavor?: WorkerId;
}
```

**States to test:**
- No featured flavor
- Featured flavor shown

### Zone 5: Flavor Roster
```tsx
// src/components/shop/FlavorRoster.tsx
interface FlavorRosterProps {
  workers: Worker[];
  featuredFlavor?: WorkerId;
  onWorkerClick: (worker: Worker) => void;
  onWorkerLongPress: (worker: Worker) => void;
}
```

**States to test:**
- All 6 workers present
- One featured (flashing border)
- One stepped back (darkened, offset)
- One removed (dithered grey, "GONE" text)
- Multiple removed

### Zone 6: Menu Bar
```tsx
// src/components/shop/MenuBar.tsx
interface MenuBarProps {
  petitionsCollected: number;
  protestUnlocked: boolean;
  onMenuAction: (action: MenuAction) => void;
  contextualActions?: ContextAction[];
}
```

**States to test:**
- Default (4 icons)
- Protest greyed (not enough signatures)
- Contextual actions active
- Morning phase (Start Day button)

