# Content System (Encounter Grammars & Templates)

**Priority:** P1
**Dependencies:** TYPE-Foundation

## Overview
Build the content system that generates agent dialogue, encounter variations, and customer interactions using grammars and templates rather than hand-written scripts.

## Content Architecture

### 1. Encounter Grammars
```typescript
// src/content/grammars/encounterGrammar.ts

interface EncounterGrammar {
  phases: {
    declaration: PhraseTemplate[];
    engagement: PhraseTemplate[];
    documentation: PhraseTemplate[];
    resolution: ResolutionTemplate[];
  };
  toneModifiers: ToneModifier[];
}

interface PhraseTemplate {
  template: string;
  variables: Record<string, VariableOption[]>;
  conditions?: TemplateCondition[];
}

type ToneModifier = {
  pressureLevel: HeatLevel;
  modifiers: string[];
  // Higher pressure = MORE politeness (escalation rule)
};
```

